patthana23.33:1.1_0: Namicchattaniyataṁ nakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paccayā sammattaniyato kusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana23.33:2.1_0: Namicchattaniyataṁ naakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paccayā micchattaniyato akusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana23.33:3.1_0: Namicchattaniyataṁ naabyākataṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca aniyato abyākato dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. (Saṅkhittaṁ.) Hetuyā cha,
